UI development tools\r\n    Ability to drive multiple initiatives at once\r\n    Team building skills\r\n    Strong software development language skill set\r\n    Languages must include, but not limited to Java, PL/SQL and JS\r\n    Broad knowledge of data exchange formats\r\n    Formats must include, but not limited to XML and JSON\r\n    Must be a powerful communicator – be able to get his/her point through\r\n    Strong problem solving and analytical skills\r\n    Experience to apply software design, implementation, testing, and debugging techniques\r\n\r\nEducation and Specifications for Web Application Developer – UI:\r\n\r\n    A Degree in Computer Science or related field\r\n    Minimum 5-7 years of software development experience\r\n    Only Singaporean / PR need to apply\r\n    Please state current / expected salary\r\n', '', '', '', 'Temporary', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Singapore', 0, 0, 'click on applu now button', NULL, '2013-06-11 02:07:20', '2013-08-30 14:46:25', '2013-07-11 02:07:20', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', NULL, NULL, '', '', 1, 1, 2),
